text:
Does anyone know if i can re-trigger `_hsq.push(['doNotTrack'])` in google tag manager when a user clicks accept?

I have this tag set up to load on pageview
```&lt;!-- Start of HubSpot Embed Code --&gt;
&lt;script type="text/javascript" id="hs-script-loader" async defer src="//js.hs-scripts.com/262138.js"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
&lt;!-- End of HubSpot Embed Code --&gt;
&lt;script&gt;
  var _hsq = _hsq || []

  if({{HubSpotDoNotTrack}} !== 'false' ) {
    _hsq.push(['doNotTrack', {
      track: true
    }]);    
  } else {
    _hsq.push(['doNotTrack']);
  }  
&lt;/script&gt;```
